  <brief_title>Treatment of Pediatric Hypertension With Altace Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Dose Escalation, Randomized, Double-blind Withdrawal Study of the Efficacy, Dose-response, and Safety of Ramipril for the Treatment of Hypertension in Children and Adolescents</official_title>
  <sponsors>
